
= "The UPB is a critical framework to guide cities to measurable impacts that can be synchronized to global PB".

=Description=

Glen:

"SRG is introducing a new conceptual framework designed for citizen’s and the commons to drive rapid whole system change inspired by Stockholm Resilience Centre and prof Johann Rockstrom’s work. The new framework will allow local actions to be correlated to global impacts in realtime by using the recently developed concept of Urban Planetary Boundaries (UPB) developed by Dr. Daniel Hoornweg of U of Toronto." 
(Loomio posting, August 2017)


